The closed interval from three to seven.

00:03:26.070 --> 00:03:28.168
So when we look at this closed interval,

00:03:28.168 --> 00:03:31.821
we're definitely continuous
over the interval.

00:03:31.821 --> 00:03:35.684
So we meet the second criteria,
but are we differentiable?

00:03:35.684 --> 00:03:38.099
Well, a good giveaway of
a point that is continuous

00:03:38.099 --> 00:03:40.288
