slope of a tangent line here.

00:03:47.660 --> 00:03:50.966
Would it be that, would it
be that, would it be that?

00:03:50.966 --> 00:03:53.622
And so because we aren't
differentiable at that point,

00:03:53.622 --> 00:03:55.222
at x is equal to six,

00:03:55.222 --> 00:03:57.365
we aren't differentiable
over this open interval

00:03:57.365 --> 00:03:59.207
