00:04:45.262 --> 00:04:47.526
at negative three and at two,

00:04:47.526 --> 00:04:49.624
over the open interval,

00:04:49.624 --> 00:04:53.352
it does look like we are both
differentiable and continuous.

00:04:53.352 --> 00:04:55.948
So we're definitely differentiable
over the open interval.

00:04:55.948 --> 00:04:59.238
But clearly, we're not continuous
